                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Chargé <persName type="from">Eddy</persName> to the <gloss
                            type="to">Secretary of State</gloss>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.—Paraphrase.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">American Embassy</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">St. Petersburg</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1905-11-13">
                            <hi rend="italic">November 13, 1905</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>(Mr. Eddy reports that an imperial proclamation was issued to-day suspending the
                    operation of the new constitution in Poland until the present disorders shall
                    cease.)</p>
            </div>
        </body>
